Package: ggseg.meshes
Title: Additional Brain Surface Meshes for the 'ggsegverse' Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
Description: Provides additional brain surface meshes for cortical and
    cerebellar visualisation in the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Cortical meshes
    include 'fsaverage5' pial, white, semi-inflated, sphere, smoothwm, and
    orig surfaces. Cerebellar meshes include the 'SUIT' flatmap surface.
    All meshes follow the same vertices/faces data frame format used by
    'ggseg.formats' and 'ggseg3d'.
